Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:36.73,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)\a6}A.I.R.nesSub 2009
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}Vermelha(紅) 在12年前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1500,990)}Vermelha(紅) 的現場直播
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}您現在看到的是押送Michiko Malandro被告的護送車
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}前科累累 對相關场所屢次進行襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}雖然被告本人對此予以否認 但是被告的其它罪行不斷曝光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.93,0:01:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}今天將被收監於Diamandra監獄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}提起Diamandra 那是關押那些改過自新無望的重刑犯的陸上孤島
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}她想重獲自由 恐怕只有等到死后了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}值得信賴的新晉升的少尉 Atsuko Jackson巡查
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:02:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}就這次的成果而言 她的努力是不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:02:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 你很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(570,405)\fs48}無視規矩的焦糖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,403號 有人探監
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很精神嘛 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我升職做巡查部長了 了不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 是你啊 Jumbo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jumbo？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你逃掉的 絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次脫獄已經是第3次了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在一步步地前進哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對甩了你的男人 那么戀戀不舍么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發春的騷貨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Atsuko 你丫小時被我扁的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴上說不要 卻用陶醉的眼神看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個變態！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會扁你的 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什么！你這個婊子！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰被誰甩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Atsuko 你丫...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫給我等著！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ina Teles、Vinicio yazik、Elena Yugi、Jucelino Bielo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}爆炸發生在圣胡安(San Juan)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}以上播報的是在巴士爆炸事件中已經確認身份的乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}雖然與本事件的關系尚不明朗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}非法組織“黑色怪物(Monstro Preto)”的成員Hiroshi Morenos的死亡也被確認
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才電視上說了什么？ 說了什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD8F5FE&\pos(500,1000)}三月17日 扁豆鎮(lentilha)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}扁豆鎮(lentilha)發生搶劫案件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}自稱是Michiko Malandro的女人挾持顧客做人質 閉門不出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}現在已經對峙了大約快1個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}犯人有可能是監獄編號為403的犯人 現在確認中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里是特別班 正在趕往現場 大約30分鐘后抵達現場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂叫個屁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾天不見發福了嘛 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了 Michiko Malandro
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回Diamandra監獄去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么是Diamandra監獄？ 我不是Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 肥豬 你聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是讓我空歡喜一場的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怨就怨自己報過Michiko這個名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana Belenbauza Yamada
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看吧 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛的 這個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H52EDFA&\pos(700,940)}三月17日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H52EDFA&\pos(600,1080)}距離橘子鎮(Laranja) 352km
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko Malandro
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個剛才聽過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你到底想問什么呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么... 難道不很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不清你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道你有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息 休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你的老爸很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro神父嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父親是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你提了個好問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi Morenos
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說說看 Hiroshi Morenos
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi... Morenos
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽名字就是個帥哥 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帥 又溫柔 我一下子就中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我這樣的女人啊 一下子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他走了 連告別都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算去見Hiroshi 現在他在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道點什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 你不是說他死了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:07:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 巴士爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么去見他是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么見？ 你是指去死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 把別人的話聽到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后？ 但是事情已經完了...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi因為爆炸事件死掉已經是11年前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幾歲？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9歲 下個月就10歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.66,0:08:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11減9
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪里搞錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞錯了？ 你說我搞錯了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫當我是傻瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把裙子掀起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吧？ 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽話！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想給別人看自己的肚臍眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老爸是那么地可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我是在問你 沒有油到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一滴都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你開個屁加油站啊 一滴總是有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我問你 就憑一滴你的摩托能開嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直向前走 有個不大的鎮子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫竊賊鎮(Ladrao)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那里的市場去的話 價格雖然會貴些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是會有的 汽油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直向前？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步行的話 3個小時左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喝嗎？ Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個... 請不要叫我Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是Hana吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且剛才我就在看 你付錢了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么吧 這點小事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔在看著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓶子碎渣 誰去收拾？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我去收拾的話 你就給我看肚臍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 Ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chin
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chin？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎摩托的女人來了 那你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算伏擊她 離開了座位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:11:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果打錯算盤 那個家伙從窗戶沖了進來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從客廳用獵槍向她射擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4發？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐是警察嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,官很大嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛從竊賊鎮(Ladrao)附近的加油站
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人舉報稱 有疑似是Michiko Malandro的女子出現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還帶著一名少女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全隊出動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,950)\c&H7CFAFA&}竊賊鎮(ladrao)的集市
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛讓我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 就像這樣凝視著我 Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他的手就伸到我的胸脯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的耳朵經常清潔啊 真的很像他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫的鼻子怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像啊 說起來你的下巴看上去也有點讓人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是相當讓人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些“零件”是從哪里(繼承)來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 你還是搞錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒... 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被這個孩子給拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日復一日 看著這照片上孩子的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管過多少年 我都不會認錯人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如你搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如我身上沒有紋身的話 你要怎么辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你丟掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我 也沒有閑到會帶著別人的孩子到處亂跑的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}關于今晨的綁架事件 出現了意想不到的嫌疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}闖入橘子鎮(Laranja)郊外圣佩德羅教堂的居住區
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}綁架9歲的Belenbauza Yamada家的次女Hana的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}現在逃跑中的兇殘嫌疑犯被正式認定為越獄犯Michiko Malandro
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}犯罪的目標是教會 手段大膽而兇殘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}這個事件對于市民社會來說 這是不可饒恕的挑釁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}當局正在盡全力繼續搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}雖然犯罪動機尚不明確 這次的事件被認為是以贖金為目的綁架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什么我都會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發過誓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 有嗎（紋身）？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 剛才有個帶小孩的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 剛剛走了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用怕 是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾啊 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快嘛 Jumbo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又變大了吧 Jumbo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許叫我Jumbo！ 你這個婊子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婊子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫從小到現在什么都沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦子里的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 你也配說別人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情叫“眼屎笑鼻屎(五十步笑百步)”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼屎？正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個鼻屎女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臟東西積累的太多 變得黑乎乎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 我要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧 Atsuko 這樣太不成體統了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人！ 現在立刻放開小孩 自首吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在什么地方遇到過你嗎 好像見過你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana 回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,養育費怎么辦啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我被欠債給逼死嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有你是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很疼愛你的嗎 Hana！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你 你不相信我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個毒蛇婦! 母豬！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主是不會袖手旁觀的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小Michiko～ 一邊走～ 一邊拉褲子～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 Atsuko
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這么無聊地結束了 多沒勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你件好事 側耳過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是你想知道的男人的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓路！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有和你玩玩了 我很爽 Atsuko
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再會了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓牢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保險金
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:17:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana在這里死掉的話 就有保險金進賬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃開！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.67,0:18:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怨恨我 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 死了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin 你丫在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是眼淚還是鼻涕啊 黏糊糊的好惡心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音都哽咽了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin算是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chin是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好嗎 Hatchin這個名字 很可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko... 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說謊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指紋身的事情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過我相信你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.91,0:20:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是因為什么被關進監獄的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都沒做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點任而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點... 嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你的朋友唱的那首歌是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰... 在還是小鬼的時候總有過失敗吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 你剛才直呼了我的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}待續
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:22.50,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}追いかけて　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:33.54,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}零れそうな星の降る夜に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:36.56,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}信じたくなる起こらない奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:42.88,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}僕とあいつの真ん中にいつも居た 君の横顔をずっと見ていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.08,0:21:45.51,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}君のすぐ隣のBest Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:48.18,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}僕の胸に仕舞い込んだ本音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:53.49,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}もし今ここで伝えたら　この世界は姿を変えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:58.49,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}神様は信じないだけど　星に願いを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:04.58,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}もう君に会いたくて　眠れない夜思いを募る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.77,0:22:07.09,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a2}Baby I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:18.15,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}寂しさを　切なさも　君と出会い　気付いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.39,0:22:23.96,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}いつも探してる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:33.08,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}Ah... Best Friend 抱き締めたい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:22.50,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}追赶着 追赶着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:33.54,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}在摇摇欲坠的星星落下的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:36.56,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}相信会发生却没有发生的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:42.88,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}我一直注视着总是处在我和他之间的你的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.08,0:21:45.51,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}我是你近在咫尺的Best Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:48.18,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}埋藏于我心间的真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:53.49,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}如果现在就在这里传达的话 这个世界的样貌会改变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:58.49,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}虽然我不相信神 但是还是向星星许了愿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:04.58,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}太想见你 无眠的夜晚累积着对你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:18.15,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}在与你邂逅之后才发觉寂寞、伤感的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.39,0:22:23.96,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}一直在找寻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:33.08,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}Ah... Best Friend 想抱紧你


